    {
      "id": "PopularPost128528",
      "post_content": "This card has saved my life about a hundred times. Overall though, I rarely use its 2nd or 3rd options, but I'll admit they're nice to have. It let's me breathe a little easier having it in my hand while in a multiplayer game, since it's very hard to kill me if all your creatures can't deal combat damage or your best spell gets fizzled.  \n  \nThe rest of the people in my group have realized this, and even if I have no blockers and nothing but two mana open and only a single card in my hand, as long as I keep cool they just mutter \"Dawn charm\" and attack someone else instead, despite me playing only one copy.",
