    {
      "id": "PopularPost162520",
      "post_content": "Three potentially game saving functions in one 2 cmc card. Like someone else said, this is one of the best candidates for [Isochron Scepter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Isochron Scepter) due to it's utility:  \n  \nChoose one:  \n[Holy Day](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day)  \n[Regenerate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Regenerate)  \nor a limited Counterspell (which admittedly doesn't effect as much as you'd hope)  \n  \nOn a Scepter, that turns your deck into Turbo Fog against creature decks, saves your most important creatures against most destruction (especially since more and more people use [Doom Blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade) instead of [Terror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror)), and can counter against burn decks.",
      "posted_by": "AssKickingBoots",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost162520\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">Three potentially game saving functions in one 2 cmc card. Like someone else said, this is one of the best candidates for <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Isochron Scepter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Isochron Scepter\">Isochron Scepter</a> due to it's utility:<br/><br/>Choose one:<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Holy Day\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day\">Holy Day</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Regenerate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Regenerate\">Regenerate</a><br/>or a limited Counterspell (which admittedly doesn't effect as much as you'd hope)<br/><br/>On a Scepter, that turns your deck into Turbo Fog against creature decks, saves your most important creatures against most destruction (especially since more and more people use <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doom Blade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade\">Doom Blade</a> instead of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror\">Terror</a>), and can counter against burn decks.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '162520'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy5